ChaosEngine.java
Sender.java

/Receiver
DSPacket.java
ChaosEngine.java
Receiver.java

cd Sender
javac *.java

cd Receiver
javac *.java

The receiver must be launched using:

java Receiver <sender_ip> <sender_ack_port> <rcv_data_port> <output_file> <RN>

The sender must be launched using:

java Sender <rcv_ip> <rcv_data_port> <sender_ack_port> <input_file> <timeout_ms> <window_size>
